Interface Dataset

All Known Subinterfaces:
FeatureClass, FeatureDataset, GeoDataset, ImageCatalog, ImageClass, ImageServer, MapDataset, RemoteFeatureClass, Table
All Known Implementing Classes:
BaseDataset, BaseFeatureClass, BaseGeoDataset, BaseImageClassProxy, BaseImageDirectoryCatalog, BaseImageFile, BaseImageServer, BaseMapDataset, DbaseTable, ShapefileDataset, ShapefileFeatureClass
public interface Dataset

Manages the retrieval of data from a local or remote data source. Any errors that are encountered by a dataset are fired as ErrorEvents to registered ErrorListeners.
